<F P=101> LATVIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Latvian Green Party Holds Conference </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Latvian Green Party Holds Conference </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1212A Riga LABRIT in Latvian 18 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1212A </F>
