<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Agency Views Paper Recycling Impact on Environment </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WN0265B Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE in Danish 19 Apr 94 
p III 4 </F>

