|ted hydrocarbons, |                  |                  |                  | 
|hydrocarbons      |                  |                  |                  | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|phenols, benzene, |sand              |residential area  |small area        | 
|toluene, xylene   |                  |                  |                  | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|polynuclear aroma-|coarse clay       |road, parking lot |limited residenti-| 
|tic hydrocarbons  |                  |                  |al area           | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|heavy metals      |clay              |industrial estate |large industrial  | 
|                  |                  |                  |areas             | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|multiple contamin-|In increasing order of amenability                      | 
|ation, e.g., hydr-|                                                        | 
|ocarbons, benzene,|                                                        | 
| toluene, xylene, |                                                        | 
|heavy metals      |                                                        | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 



</TEXT>

