environmentalist magazine in Albania. It is an organ of the 
Association for the Protection and Preservation of the Nature, 
sponsored by European Community. The newspaper will be 
published once in a three month [period] and will cover problems 
of the preservation and protection of the nature in Albania and 
in the world. 

