<H3> <TI>   Catalytic Converter Eliminates Oxides With UV Light </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Catalytic Converter Eliminates Oxides With UV Light </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR0905141694 Amsterdam TECHNISCH WEEKBLAD in Dutch 30 Mar 94 
p 1 </F>

<F P=103> BR0905141694 </F>
<F P=104>  Amsterdam TECHNISCH WEEKBLAD </F>
