<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Legislator Accuses U.S. Firms of Dumping Harmful Waste </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW0506113794 Taipei China Broadcasting Corporation News 
Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW0506113794 </F>
<F P=104>  Taipei China Broadcasting Corporation News 
Network </F>

<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


