<H3> <TI>   Water Quality Said Endangered by Autonomy Agreement </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Water Quality Said Endangered by Autonomy Agreement </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0106105394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1000 GMT 1 
