<H3> <TI>   Waste from Dual System To Be Used as Raw Materials </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Waste from Dual System To Be Used as Raw Materials </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94wn0254e Duesseldorf VDI NACHRICHTEN in German No 13, 1 Apr 
94 p 2 </F>

<F P=103> 94wn0254e </F>
<F P=104>  Duesseldorf VDI NACHRICHTEN </F>
