<H3> <TI>   New Procedures Developed for Recycling Plastics </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Procedures Developed for Recycling Plastics </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WN0254A Duesseldorf VDI NACHRICHTEN in German No 13, 1 Apr 
94 p 25 </F>

<F P=103> 94WN0254A </F>
<F P=104>  Duesseldorf VDI NACHRICHTEN </F>
