<H3> <TI>   Boom Seen for Recyclers with Great Increased Demand Forecast </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Boom Seen for Recyclers with Great Increased Demand Forecast </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WN0291B Duesseldorf VDI NACHRICHTEN in German No. 19, 13 
May 94 p 1 </F>

