  [Text] Between 8 March and 10 April, an extensive outbreak 
of diarrhea occurred in Ban Hong La-eng, Ban Uthai, Ban Toumlan, 
Ban Chengsoun, and Ban Meung in Toumlan District, Saravane 
Province. A total of 188 people were afflicted with the 
